15 int find_index(const std::vector<T> vec, const T val)
16 {
17  auto itr = std::find(vec.begin(), vec.end(), val);
18  if (itr == vec.end())
19  return -1;
20  else
21  return std::distance(vec.begin(), itr);
22 }

37  // *************************************************************************
38  bool planner::setStartJoint(std::string group_name, std::vector<double> jnt)
39  {
40  if (!isValidGroup(group_name)) return false;
41 
42  if (jnt.size()==0)
43  {
44  move_group[group_name]->setStartStateToCurrentState();
45  return true;
46  }
47 
48  sensor_msgs::JointState joint;
49  joint.name = move_group[group_name]->getJointNames();
50  if (joint.name.size()!=jnt.size()) return false;
51  joint.position = jnt;
52  auto state_p = move_group[group_name]->getCurrentState(1.0);
53  state_p->setVariableValues(joint);
54  move_group[group_name]->setStartState(*state_p.get());
55  return true;
56  }

65  joint.position = jnt;

69  // *************************************************************************
70  bool planner::waitForUpdate(std::string obj_name, bool is_known, bool is_attached, float timeout)
71  {
72  ros::Time start = ros::Time::now();
73  ros::Duration dur = ros::Time::now()-start;
74  while(ros::ok() && (dur.sec < timeout) )
75  {
76  auto attachedObj = planning_scene_interface.getAttachedObjects();
77  auto knownObj = planning_scene_interface.getKnownObjectNames();
78  bool is_attached_ = (attachedObj.count(obj_name)!=0);
79  bool is_known_ = (find_index(knownObj, obj_name)!=-1);
80  if( (is_attached_ == is_attached) && (is_known_ == is_known) )
81  return true;
82 
83  ros::Duration(0.01);
84  dur = ros::Time::now()-start;
85  }
86  return false;
87  }

106  // *************************************************************************
107  bool planner::plan(std::string group_name, std::vector<double> goal, std::vector<double> start)
108  {
109  if( !setStartJoint(group_name, start) )
110  {
111  std::cerr << "[plan] start joint setting error." << std::endl;
112  return false;
113  }
114 
115  if( !setGoalJoint(group_name, goal) )
116  {
117  std::cerr << "[plan] goal joint setting error." << std::endl;
118  return false;
119  }
120 
121  MoveGroupInterface::Plan my_plan;
122  if(move_group[group_name]->plan(my_plan) == MoveItErrorCode::SUCCESS)
123  {
124  // 成功
125  std::cerr << "[plan] success." << std::endl;
126  std::cerr << "[plan] planning time = " << my_plan.planning_time_ << std::endl;;
127  return true;
128  }
129  std::cerr << "[plan] planning failed." << std::endl;
130  return false;
131  }

135  bool planner::addBoxObject(std::string group_name, std::string object_name, std::vector<geometry_msgs::Pose> Pose, std::vector<geometry_msgs::Vector3> Size, std::vector<moveit_msgs::ObjectColor> Color)
136  {
137  if (!isValidGroup(group_name)) return false;
138  if (Pose.size() != Size.size()) return false;
139 
140  moveit_msgs::CollisionObject collision_object;
141  collision_object.header.frame_id = move_group[group_name]->getPlanningFrame();
142  collision_object.id = object_name;
143  collision_object.operation = moveit_msgs::CollisionObject::ADD;
144 
145  shape_msgs::SolidPrimitive primitive;
146  primitive.type = primitive.BOX;
147  primitive.dimensions.resize(3);
148 
149  for(int i=0; i<Pose.size(); i++)
150  {
151  primitive.dimensions[0] = Size[i].x;
152  primitive.dimensions[1] = Size[i].y;
153  primitive.dimensions[2] = Size[i].z;
154  collision_object.primitives.push_back(primitive);
155  collision_object.primitive_poses.push_back(Pose[i]);
156  }
157 
158  std::vector<moveit_msgs::CollisionObject> collision_objects;
159  collision_objects.push_back(collision_object);
160  planning_scene_interface.addCollisionObjects(collision_objects, Color);
161  return waitForUpdate(object_name, true, false, 4.0);
162  }

164  // *************************************************************************
165  bool planner::remObject(std::string object_name)
166  {
167  auto knownObj = planning_scene_interface.getKnownObjectNames();
168  if (find_index(knownObj, object_name)==-1)
169  return true; // Not defined
170 
171  std::vector<std::string> objs;
172  objs.push_back(object_name);
173  planning_scene_interface.removeCollisionObjects(objs);
174  return waitForUpdate(object_name, false, false, 4.0);
175  }
